title: Spacious Luxury 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Apartment Downtown
posting_body: ['Atrium Downtown apartments are located in the popularly sought after Walnut Creek, California.', 'This serene and pet-friendly property allows you to relax and unwind while you collect your thoughts and plan your future.', 'We offer furniture rental in cooperation with Cort Furniture Rental, to make your move to Atrium Downtown easy and hassle-free.', 'Your lease includes free membership in the S-Club, which provides upscale amenities like package delivery services, and access to your own personal concierge.', 'Let us take the stress out of city living by offering you a refuge from the noise and crowds.', 'Come home to a sparkling pool with sun deck and lounge chairs, a fitness club, and a relaxing jetted spa.', 'Walk to BART or enjoy the dining and shopping at Broadway Center.', 'We have it all at Atrium Downtown!', 'OFFICE HOURS:', 'Tuesday:\u2002\u2002 10:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday:\u2002\u2002 10:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday:\u2002\u2002 10:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday:\u2002\u2002 10:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday:\u2002\u2002 2:00pm to 6:00pm', 'PROPERTY AMENITIES:', '* Pool', '* Hot Tub', '* Concierge Services', '* Package Receiving', '* Short Term Lease', '* Storage Space', '* Fitness Center', '* On-site Maintenance', '* Sundeck', '* Elevator', '* High Speed Internet Available', '* Near Public Transit', '* Controlled Access', '* Parking', '* Near Broadway Plaza', '* Courtyard with mature trees', '* Jet spa', '* Easy access to Highway 680, 24 & to BART', '* Laundry center', 'Website: <URL> Leasing URL:', '<URL>', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'Address: 1812 Trinity Avenue Walnut Creek, CA 94596', 'Managed By: Sequoia Equities, Inc.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers']
